examples.en: We stayed in the hotel's honeymoon suite.
All the hotel's bedrooms are light and airy.
The hotel's chef trained at the finest culinary institutes in Europe.
The hotel's award-winning restaurant specializes in traditional food.
The hotel's owners see to it that their guests are given every luxury.
Guests who stay in the hotel's most expensive suite live in monarchical splendor.
The hotel's shabby, outdated exercise room was its paltry attempt at a health spa.
After complaining about the hotel's lousy service, the woman went off on another rant about the condition of her room.
